'''聖伯多祿義大利人教堂'''（St. Peter's Italian Church）是位於[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]][[霍本|霍本]]的一座[[巴西利卡|巴西利卡]]風格的教堂<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.italianchurch.org.uk/DOCS/PDF/Stpeters.PDF |title=St Peter's Italian church images |accessdate=2017-02-14 |archive-date=2010-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101224085912/http://www.italianchurch.org.uk/DOCS/PDF/Stpeters.PDF |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。教堂修建於19世紀中期<ref name="BBCLondon1">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/london/content/articles/2005/05/26/italian_community_feature.shtml   Italian London] ''[[BBC_London|BBC London]]'', 02/07/2008, 12:25UK (Accessed 27/08/2008)</ref>。正面有一座33米高的鐘樓，修建於1891年。現在教堂仍是當地義大利人社區的中心。

